item.title: Timur Mutsurayev (Тимур Муцураев) 3x
item.description: Mutsurayev, whether he wants it or not, is forever a friend of the Russian language. And of Russian-language songs. Here are three, and let’s be honest. Candles Extinguished Tekst On YouTube, there’s also a static clip. Living room versions by, among others, Васяга (2018) and Тимур И Жанна (2012).
